92-- ----------------------  Data
93
94-- | Strict bytestring.
95type Bs = Data.ByteString.ByteString
96
97-- | Convert strict bytestring to string.
98--   This is same as 'Data.ByteString.UTF8.toString'.
99bsString :: Bs -> String
100bsString = Data.ByteString.UTF8.toString
101
102-- | Convert string to strict bytestring.
103--   This is same as 'Data.ByteString.UTF8.fromString'.
104stringBs :: String -> Bs
105stringBs = Data.ByteString.UTF8.fromString
106
107-- | Lazy bytestring.
108type Bz = Data.ByteString.Lazy.ByteString
109
110-- | Convert string into lazy bytestring.
111--   This is same as 'Data.ByteString.Lazy.UTF8.fromString'.
112stringBz :: String -> Bz
113stringBz = Data.ByteString.Lazy.UTF8.fromString
114
115-- | Convert lazy bytestring to string.
116--   This is same as 'Data.ByteString.Lazy.UTF8.toString'.
117bzString :: Bz -> String
118bzString = Data.ByteString.Lazy.UTF8.toString
119
120-- | Convert strict text to string.
121--   This is same as 'Data.Text.unpack'.
122txString :: O.Tx -> String
123txString = Data.Text.unpack
124
125-- | Convert string to strict text.
126--   This is same as 'Data.Text.pack'.
127stringTx :: String -> O.Tx
128stringTx = Data.Text.pack
129
130-- | Convert lazy text to string.
131--   This is same as 'Data.Text.Lazy.unpack'.
132tzString :: O.Tz -> String
133tzString = Data.Text.Lazy.unpack
134
135-- | Convert string to lazy text.
136--   This is same as 'Data.Text.Lazy.pack'.
137stringTz :: String -> O.Tz
138stringTz = Data.Text.Lazy.pack
139
140-- | Same as 'Map.lookup' in @Data.Map@ module.
141lookupMap :: (Ord k) => k -> Data.Map.Map k a -> Maybe a
142lookupMap = Data.Map.lookup
143
144
145-- ----------------------  Text
146
147-- | Same as 'Text.PrettyPrint.empty'.
148docEmpty :: Text.PrettyPrint.Doc
149docEmpty = Text.PrettyPrint.empty
150
151-- | Same as 'Text.PrettyPrint.hang'.
152docHang :: Text.PrettyPrint.Doc -> Int -> Text.PrettyPrint.Doc -> Text.PrettyPrint.Doc
153docHang = Text.PrettyPrint.hang
154
155-- | Same as 'Text.PrettyPrint.zeroWidthText'.
156docZero :: String -> Text.PrettyPrint.Doc
157docZero = Text.PrettyPrint.zeroWidthText
